text: Arabella Morton (born 18 November 2000) is an Australian actress, best known for her role as Gael in the fantasy adventure film The Chronicles of Narnia: The Voyage of the Dawn Treader (2010), based on the 1952 novel The Voyage of the Dawn Treader.
